com.robopupu.api.graph.nodes

Class ListNode<IN>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.graph.Node<IN,IN>
      • com.robopupu.api.graph.nodes.ListNode<IN>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputNode<IN>, OutputNode<IN>

    public class ListNode<IN>
extends Node<IN,IN>
    ListNode either emits all the values from a given List (immutable version), or the input values that are received and stored to a List until Node.onCompleted(OutputNode) is invoked (mutable version).
